  <brief_title>Epidemiology, Costs and Psychosocial Consequences of Genital Warts in Valparaiso, Chile</brief_title>
  <official_title>Genital Warts: Studies for Establishing Epidemiological Profile, Psychosocial Consequences and Costs of Disease in Attendants to the Sexual Health Clinic of the Public Health Service of Valparaiso and San Antonio, Chile.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
